001package io.ebean.plugin;
002
003import io.ebean.bean.EntityBean;
004
005/**
006 * Property of a entity bean that is a ToMany property.
007 */
008public interface PropertyAssocMany extends Property {
009
010  /**
011   * Add the loaded current bean to its associated parent.
012   * <p>
013   * Helper method used by Ebean Elastic integration when loading with a persistence context.
014   */
015  void lazyLoadMany(EntityBean current);
016}
